    "text": "Incident Report Form Use this form to record a server problem, exploit, outage, data loss, hacked account, or other serious event. Use for outages, crashes, exploits, data loss, security concerns, major moderation events, and other operational incidents. Incident identity Incident title: Incident ID: Severity: SEV 1 / SEV 2 / SEV 3 / SEV 4 Status: Investigating / Contained / Recovering / Monitoring / Resolved Incident Lead: Scribe: Start time and timezone: Detection time and timezone: Resolution time and timezone: Summary What happened? Player/service impact: Affected systems/worlds/features: Known data loss or corruption: Timeline Time Person/System Event, observation, command, or decision Evidence and diagnostics Logs: Metrics/profiles: Screenshots/video: Backups/snapshots: Recent changes: Related tickets/cases: Actions Containment Recovery Final Checks Communication Initial notice: Updates: Resolution notice: Approver: Root cause and review Root cause: Contributing factors: What worked: What failed: Compensation/reconciliation: Corrective action Owner Due date Status"
